headline: The Home Depot, Inc. (HD) Remains a Key Pick as TD Cowen Updates Hardlines Outlook
summary: The Home Depot, Inc. (NYSE:HD) is included among Dividend Contenders List: Top 20 Stocks. On January 20, TD Cowen analyst Max Rakhlenko raised the firm’s price target on The Home Depot, Inc.
